Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.86,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,BAKAR
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:41.04,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,KUKIS BESAR YANG DIBUAT SECARA KHUSUS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:51.68,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,PERLENGKAPAN OLAHRAGA
