Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.44,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,4 APRIL
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.69,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,6 FEBRUARI
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.19,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,3 MARET
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.07,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,3 JANUARI
