Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:19.20,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,CAIM TANGGAL 5 JULI
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:26.33,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,13 SEPTEMBER!
