Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah repot-repot\Nmau datang, Iruma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan tuangkan teh dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Bapak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Imut sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu saat orang tuaku\Nmerayakan ulang tahunku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, aku ingin kamu dengar\Nsedikit tentangku pada saat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Info ini akan bermanfaat bagi manusia\Nyang tinggal di sini sepertimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Ritual Iblis Suzuki Iruma".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sedang apa?\NAyo pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada daun di kepalamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu menyembunyikan sesuatu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak boleh! Aku bisa langsung tahu\Nsaat kamu bohong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo cepat keluarkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi-lagi dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kembalikan dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma lihat sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak boleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu itu kamu juga bilang begitu,\Ntapi malah dibawa pulang dan dimainin terus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak cukup umur, aku selalu tertarik\Npada makhluk hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa cara berjalannya berbeda denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dia punya tiga ekor,\Ntapi matanya hanya satu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku makin bersemangat\Nketika meneliti lebih jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keinginan untuk mengenal\Nmakhluk-makhluk asing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau membuatku penasaran,\Naku akan segera menganalisisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh, Shichiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah berapa kali dibilang,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jangan dibawa pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tuaku sering memarahiku begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang tidak bisa paham\Ntanpa melihat langsung.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semangatku akan pengetahuan tidak terhentikan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin lebih dalam lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat sadar, aku berada\Ndi atas seribu ranting layu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata itu sarang\Nmilik seekor burung raksasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, setelah semalam berlalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, aku ingin makan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di saat itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama kalinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku paham kalau\Nmakhluk hidup itu indah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luka di mulutku ini\Nkarena ibu burung yang marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tuaku berhasil menyelamatkanku\Ntepat waktu,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku kena marah besar setelahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku merenungkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tuaku selalu marah\Nbukan karena aku tidak menuruti mereka,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi karena aku terlalu ceroboh atas nyawaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alasan ibu burung yang melindungi telurnya\Nsekuat tenaga terlihat indah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena nyawa adalah\Nhal yang sangat berharga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di dunia iblis,\Nbanyak yang ceroboh atas nyawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang begitu tatanannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kurasa lebih baik\Naku membagikan pengalaman pertamaku
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}agar kamu paham betapa\Nmenyeramkannya itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf tiba-tiba aku cerita begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah menghabiskan waktu\Nbersama para iblis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}betapa jujurnya mereka\Npada keinginan mereka,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan memberikan segalanya\Npada apa yang mereka ingin lakukan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka terlihat sungguh berkilauan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga berpikir semua iblis itu indah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, aku sangat paham\Nperkataan Bapak dan sangat tersentuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku inginnya kamu lebih takut, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Soalnya kamu terlalu santai, Iruma.\N- Lo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dapat laporan mengkhawatirkan\Ndari Asmodeus dan Kalego.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka membuatku khawatir, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan pernah lupakan\Nsemangat pemulamu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berinteraksilah dengan penuh perhatian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, saling mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Supaya kamu bisa hidup bersama kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita perlu saling mengenal lebih lagi, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\NBapak ingin tahu apa tentangku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan ulang tahunmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ulang tahunku itu 4 Oktober!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu, ya.\N4 Okto—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makan malam hari ini apa, ya?\NApakah makanan favoritnya Iruma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau tidak salah,\Ndia juga suka itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Opera, ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku barusan dapat telepon dari Balam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Iruma... Tuan Iruma...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ulang tahun Tuan Iruma...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}4 Oktober.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ulang tahun Tuan Iruma...\N- Ulang tahun Irumachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- tanggal 4 Oktober?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita kelewatan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari itu pagi yang damai seperti biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakek! Opera! Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, tidak ada orang...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba, mataku ditutup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampaknya aku dibawa\Nke suatu tempat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat sudah sadar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tampaknya ada\Ndi tengah ritual yang luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iruma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu terkejut?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakek!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena ini acara besar cucuku,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku jadi bersemangat mempersiapkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapel yang bagus, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Acara apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja acara yang sangat cocok\Nuntuk Tuan Iruma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Irumachi, hawehya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azz! Clara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hawehya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan Kak Ameri juga ada!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dapat telepon dari Pak Balam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak kusangka aku\Nmelewatkan ritual iblis Anda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan tidak tahu\Nkapan ulang tahun Anda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku gagal sebagai sahabat Anda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu harusnya kasih tahu sejak awal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ritual iblis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Ritual Iblis".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu adalah ritual perayaan\Nulang tahun iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para tamu memberikan persembahan,\Nmengenakan kostum,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}serta bernyanyi dan menari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kata lain, dalam bahasa manusia,\Nini adalah pesta ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga dirayakan saat umurku enam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski hanya di rumah kecil\Nyang terbengkalai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, aku juga dirayakan di umur yang sama!\NPersembahanku dicuri kakakku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena tidak boleh mencolok,\Naku pakai kostum biasa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebanyakan iblis\Ntidak merayakannya tiap tahun, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, ini pertama kalinya\Naku melihat ritual semegah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh cocok untuk rivalku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan, ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini perayaan ulang tahunmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kota asalmu unik dan adatnya beda,\Njadi ini menarik, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hadiah dari Ame besar juga, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya ini ultahnya Irumachi!\NAku juga bawa banyak hadiah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harap Iruma senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Percaya diri total.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hawehya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari meriahkan hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo, Kalego ada di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya dia harus merawat kaktus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perkamen pemanggilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taruh di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Sip" ndasmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu selalu saja begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah, mustahil kamu tidak dipanggil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nkarena semua tamunya sudah hadir,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mari kita mulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hawehya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hawehya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, hawehya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Weh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}La Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Airnya terbakar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku harus melakukan sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kamu tak perlu melakukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bang Ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam ritual iblis,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}air yang disebut "air mana"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}digunakan untuk menyalakan api.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu melambangkan jiwa-jiwa\Nyang hadir dalam ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, mereka akan satu per satu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menuang air api itu ke bejana besar\Ndi depan sang tokoh utama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seolah membagi\Napi kehidupan mereka padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, memberi hadiah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan mengucapkan selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Iruma, aku sangat bersyukur\NAnda dilahirkan dan hidup di dunia iblis ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini adalah aksesori yang pantas untuk Anda\Nyang sedang melangkah menuju kejayaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantel dengan jubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan diterima.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azz, terima ka—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di dunia iblis yang kejam,\Nhidup itu singkat dan berharga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ritual iblis adalah ritual rasa syukur\Natas kehidupan yang telah terlahir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, intinya kamu yang harus\Nmenerima ucapan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Irumachi! Irumachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu! Karena bingung mau kasih apa,\Nkubawa saja semua!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ingat ultahmu 4 Oktober!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena ini hari bahagia,\Naku tuangkan api yang banyak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bakar, bakar, bakar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu, hadiah dariku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, boneka kesayanganku\Ndan juga beberapa permen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari saudara dan saudariku\Nadalah gambar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sketsanya dibuat oleh Urara,\Nlalu diwarnai oleh Konchie dan Keebow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jejak tangannya dibuat oleh para bocil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dari Mami, sendal buatan tangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih selalu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tuan Iruma.\N- Irumachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tuan Iruma.\N- Irumachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iruma, ini persembahan kecil dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukis yang dibuat khusus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Besar banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima ini, Iruma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu perlengkapan olahraga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teruslah jadi rivalku yang tangguh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu penunjang potensimu\Nuntuk bersinar terang di atas panggung.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kosmetik perawatan kulit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panggung?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:16:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini jawaban dari surat yang kuterima
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saat festival musik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bawakan anting untuk orang dewasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bawa parfum wajib bagi pria sejati!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bisa tidur nyenyak dengan bantal ini, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diriku bawa penghangat perut dan syal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, Schneider bawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buku catatan untuk bantu belajar saat kelas dua!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemutar musik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang bilang niat adalah yang terpenting,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi yang penting hadiahnya disukai, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus, aku jadi bingung dan panik\Nmau memberi apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada lagu rakyat, balada,\Ndan lagu festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dengarkanlah.\NPilihan lagunya agak acak,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin kamu bakal ketagihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini biografi dunia iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir ini akan berguna\Nuntuk tinggal di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan aku baca!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku juga harus ikut-ikutan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari hari ulang tahunmu,\NMemang agak telat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi bisa bertemu\Ndan bisa bersama denganmu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuat kami bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah terlahir, Iruma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hawehya! Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hawehya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hawehya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Terima kasih, Iruma.\N- Terima kasih, Tuan Iruma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tuan Iruma!\N- Selamat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore, hore! Hawehya, Iruma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hadiah dariku adalah gim retro yang langka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ultahmu ternyata Oktober, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, ultahku September.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini artinya kamu adalah adikku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, Irumacchi menangis karenamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sangat tidak mau jadi adikku, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiada alasan lagi selain itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Iruma, Anda baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang saja, aku akan segera membakarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, kok aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sini kamu!\N- Kamu sudah siap, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah dapat\Nperayaan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga dapat banyak\Nterima kasih dari kalian semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar senang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih semuanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, apa yang kalian lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa harus memeluknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagian, kamu tidak perlu\Ntiba-tiba marah begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iblis bisa mati kalau dikejutkan\Ndengan suara keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Iruma pingsan bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasihan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sampai sebahagia itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini jadi ritual iblis yang bagus, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, aneh kamu yang berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya ini ritual saat semuanya\Nberterima kasih padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Be-Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ingin tahu ultah kalian semua\Nagar bisa mengucapkan banyak terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Aku 6 Juni!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Aku 5 Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat sekali respons kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, aku 8 Agustus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku 22 Desember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku 7 Juni.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku 13 Maret.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}10 Deviler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diriku 4 April.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}6 Februari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}3 Maret.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}3 Januari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}4 November.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebentar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang kubilang tadi,\Naku ultah lebih dulu di bulan September.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan ini, sudah jelas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lied yang adik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kok begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Habisnya, aku September dan Iruma Oktober.\N- Mereka berdua tidak berubah, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa Pak Kalego juga punya tanggal ultah?\N- Jelas aku yang kakak, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa membayangkan beliau\Nsaat masih bayi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sepertiku\Nyang terlahir sebagai pria sejati,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}beliau pasti bayi\Nyang pemarah dan menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti kalau bayi lain menangis...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bakal dimarahi begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian seenaknya berpikir\Nyang tidak-tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu cuma spekulasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak teori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku pengin pergi ke pantai!\N- Berisiknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iruma sampai menangis bahagia\Nkarena pesta ulang tahunnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Syukurlah.\N- Kalau menangis terus, Anda akan meleleh, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, Tuan Iruma, ini waktunya\Nacara utama dari ritual ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di akhir, pemeran utamanya\Nharus memadamkan apinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditiup "Fuh" begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti kue ultah, ya!\NDi sini juga ada, toh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memadamkan api ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Iya!\N- Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Persiapannya sudah siap, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Yuk!\N- Tiup semuanya sekaligus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Lakukan!\N- Tiup semuanya sekaligus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Soalnya ini acara terakhir.\N- Semangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan, Tuan Iruma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo tiup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Irumachi, semangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak padam!\NSama sekali tidak padam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki Iruma, peringkat He,\Nkediaman dunia iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, semuanya\Nsudah berkumpul, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Lepaskan! Aku tidak perlu ikut!\N- Aku akan atur waktu kameranya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tenanglah.\N- Aku akan atur waktu kameranya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bagaimana caranya tenang?\N- Tiga, dua, satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kalego, tenanglah.\N- Tiga, dua, satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah pesta ultah yang terlambat\Nsekitar tiga minggu,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bersama teman-temannya\Nyang tak tergantikan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia mengambil langkah pertamanya\Nsebagai lelaki berusia 15 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.54,0:23:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hawehya!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iruma! Sesembahan dariku\Ndan Opera adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kue ulang tahun raksasa, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyam, nyam.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enaknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azz-Azz, ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.60,0:24:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selagi sempat, ayo kita foto bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.27,0:24:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi mendekati Iruma yang telah\Nmencapai peringkat He dan makin bersinar,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.44,0:24:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eiko melatih pikiran dan tubuhnya\Njauh di pegunungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.19,0:24:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah turun dari gunung\Ndan menerima pesan, dia pun jadi panik.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.99,0:24:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Irubo, rasanya senang dirayakan teman-teman, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.99,0:24:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah 15 tahun, ya.\NIrubo yang kecil sampai muat masuk saku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Irubo yang biasa menangis\Nsepanjang malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.87,0:24:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Irubo yang terbentur kepalanya pada kaki meja\Nsaat pertama kali merangkak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.42,0:24:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Irubo yang kata-kata\Npertamanya adalah "Bang Ali".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.38,0:24:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu berlalu sangat cepat.\NHatiku tersentuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.88,0:24:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, Selamat Datang\Ndi Sekolah Iblis, Iruma.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.63,0:24:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Menyusup ke Asrama Guru!" dan "Anggota Baru\NAcara Perkumpulan Perempuan?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.60,0:24:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teruslah tumbuh dengan baik, Irubo.
